This repository is work on progress on how to compile GDC, the GNU D Compiler,
on NetBSD 10.

Tested on amd64 with pkgsrc-2025Q4.

Structure:
- HOWTO contains the instructions.
- patches/ contains patches for libphobos-libdruntime.
  - I have submitted patches to Druntime (see dlang/dmd#22720).
- pkgsrc-mods/ contains modifications to the pkgsrc files.